version.changelog:
v0.56-beta

- FX Search: Visual optimization;
- Radial Menu: Completely eliminated any aliasing in drawing;
- Wwise Replace: Major update, one-click wav replacement + Bnk generation;
- Render Queue: Integrated with Wwise Replace;
- Region flow: Significant performance improvement;
- Trim item action: Switched to a version that preserves Fades;
- Underlying event architecture fully optimized;

-- Mantrika Team
-- 2026-04.20

